## Pipeline Event Sequence

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as API Server
    participant EventBus as ContextEventBus
    participant Pipeline as ParallelContextPipeline
    participant Cache as ContextCache
    participant DB as Database

    Client->>API: POST /context-engine/assemble
    API->>EventBus: emit('assembly:started', params)
    
    Note over EventBus: Log start time
    Note over EventBus: Emit telemetry
    
    API->>Pipeline: assembleParallel(params)
    
    Note over Pipeline: Stage 0: Parallel fetch
    Pipeline->>EventBus: emit('telemetry:assembly_start', stage)
    
    Pipeline->>Cache: getSettings(userId)
    alt Cache hit
        Cache-->>Pipeline: settings
        Pipeline->>EventBus: emit('cache:hit', 'settings')
    else Cache miss
        Pipeline->>DB: fetch settings
        DB-->>Pipeline: settings
        Pipeline->>Cache: setSettings
        Pipeline->>EventBus: emit('cache:miss', 'settings')
    end
    
    Note over Pipeline: Stage 1: Detection
    Pipeline->>EventBus: emit('telemetry:detection_start')
    
    Pipeline->>DB: semantic search topics
    Pipeline->>EventBus: emit('telemetry:detection_complete', {topics, entities})
    
    Note over Pipeline: Stage 2: Bundle compilation
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: fetchOrCompileBundle('identity_core')
    Pipeline->>EventBus: emit('telemetry:bundle_compiled', {bundleType, tokens})
    
    loop for each bundle
        Pipeline->>Cache: setBundle
        Pipeline->>EventBus: emit('cache:hit', bundleType)
    end
    
    Note over Pipeline: Stage 3: Assembly
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: compilePromptFromBundles
    Pipeline->>EventBus: emit('assembly:completed', metrics)
    
    Pipeline-->>API: AssembledContext + metrics
    API-->>Client: Response
    
    EventBus->>EventBus: aggregate_metrics
    Note over EventBus: Emit final telemetry event
```

