## WebSocket Communication Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant WS as Socket.io
    participant Context as ContextWS Service
    participant Pipeline as ParallelContextPipeline
    participant Cache as ContextCache
    participant LLM as AI Provider

    Client->>WS: connect(token)
    WS->>Context: authenticate(token)
    
    alt Authentication successful
        Context-->>WS: authenticated
        WS-->>Client: connected
    else Authentication failed
        WS-->>Client: connect_error
    end

    Note over Client: Start context assembly
    Client->>WS: start_assembly({userMessage, conversationId})
    WS->>Context: handle_start_assembly

    Context->>Pipeline: assembleStreaming(params)

    Note over Pipeline: Yield chunks in priority order
    loop Streaming chunks
        Pipeline->>Context: chunk
        Context->>Client: context_chunk
    end

    Note over Client: Partial context update request
    Client->>WS: update_context({query})
    WS->>Context: handle_update

    Context->>Pipeline: jitRetrieve(query)
    Pipeline->>Cache: check_cache
    Cache-->>Pipeline: partial_results
    Pipeline-->>Context: partial_context
    Context->>Client: context_update

    Note over Client: Close connection
    Client->>WS: disconnect
    WS->>Context: cleanup
    Context->>Cache: release_resources
```

