## Circuit Breaker Pattern

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Closed
    
    Closed --> Open: failureThreshold reached
    Closed --> HalfOpen: recoveryTimeout elapsed
    
    Open --> Closed: Test success
    Open --> Open: Test fails
    
    HalfOpen --> Closed: Test success
    HalfOpen --> Open: Test fails
    
    note right of Closed: Normal operation<br/>Requests pass through
    note right of Open: Circuit open<br/>Requests rejected immediately
    note right of HalfOpen: Testing recovery<br/>Limited requests allowed
```